snippet.title: Corsair's Madness | Release Date Annoucement!
snippet.description:
✨Add Corsair's Madness to your wishlist✨ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1829310/Corsairs_Madness/

Take on the role of the captain on a pirate ship on 17.07.2024! Travel the mystical archipelago full of secrets and treasures to save the crew members scattered around the different islands and discover the dark secrets of a mysterious temple.

📣And follow our social media📣
http://bio.link/madneticgames 

Developer: Old Prawn
Publisher: Madnetic Games
